title: fangandcallan.github.io
text:
Hi my name is Zifang. I’m from Chinese Studies. You can view my work this semester on NM2207 here.

Please check out my creative thoughts - ‘The Eyes You’ll Shut Forever’, a dialog between us and the death inmate, tapping on the character development in the The Game of Thrones, reflecting our internal journey. You can scroll down to avoid the navigation bar from disturbing the experience and get instructions.
You will also have access to the github link that contains all the files used in this sem. For the source code, data etc. for the project, you can check them at fangandcallan.github.io in the same link.

Thanks for coming to my site ~

title: The Eyes You’ll Shut Forever
text:
They are executed. But are they resting in peace?


Please view the videos before you proceed to action upon the last statements. Once you make the choice, you can get a new statement by selecting a different eye color of the death inmate. Remember, this is YOUR choice as the living to treat the dead.
